{
  "stem": "6257.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came once-- they came once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was my-- they used to come, usually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, when they were late, I would be sort of terrified because I knew nobody-- didn't know-- didn't know anybody's address.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt-- I was completely at the mercy of those people who, you know, and they were really having the-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, because it was partly money anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what they would have done.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Under the Warsaw uprisal I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No there-- there was Warsaw uprising--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year later in '44, in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the-- the Polish uprising.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it was-- you know, more or less then, or at least the Russians had come to the Vistula, more or less outside of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before that, the Germans seemed to be sort of in disarray, leaving, going east.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I could see them all, columns of them, going-- going west, rather, going-- running away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some Italians [? orders, ?] I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- and I think they were badly hoping that the Russians would come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the Russians wouldn't or didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans eventually won this fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, Warsaw was really in-- was in ruins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember sort of hiding, being in the cellar because the rest of the building was crashed down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how I also had to be-- was surprised that even there, you know, people would sort of whisper that I was Jewish and so on at that time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and also [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Vladka's ?] husband's family were-- he brought his family-- just because it seemed the end of the war somehow-- there to the same block of flats.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
